sharedAssessmentHelpCard.message:
Here you can share your assessments with your colleagues, such as tutors.
Find out which e-mail your colleague use in Google Classroom. Type the e-mail below and then click the add button. Sharing assessments means that your colleague will have full read access to your assessments provided that the teacher also has the same student in any of his/her classrooms. Your colleague will see your assessments in their student progress view.
